    "It supports convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and fully connected networks 221.",
    "Power consumption in standard tasks ranges from 100 μW to 300 mW.",
    "approach, the neuron model encodes the information in frequency output, resembling natural modulation.",
    "Using silicon neurons rather than simulated neurons will allow for the use of the output neurons as pulse generators by adding a pulse extender circuit to the output of the neuron 124.",
